cn.hutool.json

Class JSONArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • cn.hutool.json.JSONArray
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    cn.hutool.core.getter.BasicTypeGetter<Integer>, cn.hutool.core.getter.OptBasicTypeGetter<Integer>, cn.hutool.core.getter.OptNullBasicTypeFromObjectGetter<Integer>, cn.hutool.core.getter.OptNullBasicTypeGetter<Integer>, JSON, JSONGetter<Integer>, Serializable, Cloneable, Iterable<Object>, Collection<Object>, List<Object>, RandomAccess

    public class JSONArray
extends Object
implements JSON, JSONGetter<Integer>, List<Object>, RandomAccess
    JSON数组
    JSON数组是表示中括号括住的数据表现形式
    对应的JSON字符串格格式例如: 
     ["a", "b", "c", 12]
    Author:
    looly
